[[A-microgpt]]
== Appendix A: microGPT in Python ‚Äî Complete Runnable Code

This appendix assembles every Python snippet from the book into `src/python/microgpt.py`, with all dependencies resolved.
The implementation uses only the Python standard library.

=== Installation & Running

[source,bash]
----
# Run the full demo
python3 src/python/microgpt.py

# Run every chapter's end-to-end code check
bundle exec rake book:run_code
----

=== Annotated Assembly

The complete `microgpt.py` is in `src/python/microgpt.py`.
It is organized in dependency order:

1. *Matrix primitives* ‚Äî `make_matrix`, `matrix_multiply`, `matrix_add`, `matrix_scale`, `transpose`, `hstack`
2. *Activations* ‚Äî `softmax`, `softmax_rows`, `gelu`, `sigmoid`
3. *Embeddings* ‚Äî `random_matrix`, `embed_sequence`
4. *Positional encoding* ‚Äî `sinusoidal_encoding`, `add_positional_encoding`
5. *Attention* ‚Äî `scaled-dot-product-attention`, `causal-mask`
6. *Multi-head attention* ‚Äî `multi_head_attention`
7. *FFN* ‚Äî `feed_forward`
8. *Layer norm* ‚Äî `layer_norm_matrix`
9. *Transformer block* ‚Äî `transformer_block`
10. *GPT model* ‚Äî `gpt_forward`, `generate`

